Author: VirideGliridae
Text: I have the opposite problem D: My throat has apparently gotten so used to "something pushing back there" = "throw up", that I threw up a bit on my boyfriend. Not...my finest hour. Fortunately I have a very sweet and understanding man or that would've been fairly awful.

Author: Hairless_Human
Text: I'm a straight male and I have no gag reflex either. Da hell am I supposed to do with this lame super power. I also don't have the ability to barf like at all no matter what. I didn't even vomit when I ODed on caffeine. When I get sick and it feels like I might throw up I will try my hardest to but nothing comes up. Gonna suck the day I get poisoned from something and I can't use barfing to try and expel the poison.
